ABOUT

Software Engineer

My name is Paridarshan Sahoo, a B.Tech student in Computer Science and Engineering (Data Science) at Maharana Pratap Engineering College, Kanpur. I have experience in developing innovative projects like a face recognition-based attendance management system and a library management system. Notable achievements include being a finalist in the Smart India Hackathon 2023 and excelling in competitive coding events. Skilled in Python, C  and C++, I am passionate about data structures, algorithms, and machine learning. I also bring organizational and creative skills, demonstrated through event management and photography.
